ss=title> Re: Melee range</span><hr size=1> &lt;Smile&gt; It’s okay man. There is a lot going on in the Raids and most don’t really trickle down to the raiders, for different reasons. In the case of some of the changes in Vox raid it was split minute changes that had to be done in order for us to all make it to our goal. Taking Vox down. <br>
<br>
“Are plane mobs the same?”<br>
<br>
I’m not a caster so I’m not 100% on what you need to be in melee range for or not. I know Giants and Dragons are a most, I’m guessing Gods and the mini bosses are the same. As for the Random monsters in the planes, no I don’t think you need to be in Melee range. <br>
<br>
“Melee range for spells only?”<br>
<br>
All offensive spells, for Giants and dragons you need to be basically standing under them to work. I don’t know why &lt;shrug&gt; just do. Giants also can’t be Mezed but can be Charmed. <br>
<br>
“I saw you once but didn`t know your were support.”<br>
<br>
&lt;LOL&gt; Was spending a lot of time Banished or in the lair. <br>
<br>
“And didn`t know that we were getting mobs pulled to us. Thought they were the ones that snuk past support I would have been paying more attention.”<br>
<br>
Yeah we had to do a split second change there. When I noticed we didn’t have the number of people needed to tank like 4 giants and some Ice Terrors I had to call you guys in to help. There was no way I (a non-taunter) would be able to hold aggro on them all. Cleric would have died and the rest of the team shortly after. The pull didn’t really go right, The puller died and I want around the corner to pull the ones we got out of the lair to you guys and got Banished. The Mage I think tried the same think and got his pretty robe all bloody with his own blood (Didn’t aggro vox so didn’t get banished and the giants beat him to a pulp) so all that was left was the Cleric. She ran out and grabbed then and only had time to call in the INC when they all stormed in to the room. On the second pull of giants the cleric went to heal the puller and got banished. &lt;LOL&gt; That’s also the time we all had to camp for a bit because someone had healed, buffed or something the pulled and still had Vox Aggroed so she was walking from her spawn to the way out of her lair and down to the where the buffing area was. (Not a good place to have her when you’re trying to buff) I figured I would just charge some Giants on you all and you could kill them, the other option was listening to me for like 30 minutes explaining what was going on. &lt;Snicker&gt; It all worked out. I had no doubt you guys would kill the giants.<br>
<br>
And behold… Order in Chaos.<br>
<br>
